EN: He finds learning foreign languages very interesting.

ZH: 在现代社会里，懂得外语是很重要的。
EN: In modern society, knowing foreign languages is very important.

ZH: 学习外语能够帮助人们更容易地理解外国文化。
EN: Learning foreign languages can help people better understand foreign cultures.

ZH: 他每天都会花一些时间练习外语。
EN: He spends some time practicing foreign languages every day.

ZH: 去旅行的时候，懂得外语可以帮助你更好地交流。
EN: Knowing foreign languages can help you communicate better when traveling.

ZH: 学外语不仅可以拓展你的视野，还可以为你的职业发展带来机会。
EN: Learning foreign languages can not only broaden your horizons, but also bring opportunities for your career development.

ZH: 学生们被要求至少掌握一门外语。
EN: Students are required to master at least one foreign language.

ZH: 我们学校为学生提供了各种外语课程。
EN: Our school offers various foreign language courses for students.

